This paper discusses the use of wireless energy transfer (WET) technology in wireless communication, which falls under the categories of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the potential for increased throughput and flexibility, which relates to multimedia (cs.MM) and electromagnetics (cs.EM).
